th these values and comply with all relevant legislation and regulations.</p>		\n			<h2>Renowned Chefs</h2>		\n			<p>Meet the taste experts</p>		\n			<h3>Careers</h3>		\n				<h4>\n					<a href=\"#\">Be a part of our restaurant</a>\n				</h4>\n				<p></p>\n			<a href=\"http://localhost/thebbqpalace/contact-us/\" role=\"button\">\n						Apply Today\n					</a>\n			<figure><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://localhost/thebbqpalace/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Mehboob-Khan-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure><h3>Mehboob Khan</h3><p>Founder / Head Chef</p>		\n										<img width=\"200\" height=\"35\" src=\"http://localhost/thebbqpalace/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/divider-free-img-1.png\" alt=\"\" />											\n							<a href=\"\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n					Facebook\n				</a>\n							<a href=\"\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n					Twitter\n				</a>\n							<a href=\"\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n					Tripadvisor\n				</a>\n							<a href=\"\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n					Instagram\n				</a>\n			<figure><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://localhost/thebbqpalace/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Samia-Ahad-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" /></figure><h3>Samia Ahad</h3><p>Co-Founder / Chef</p>		\n										<img width=\"200\" height=\"35\" src=\"http://localhost/thebbqpalace/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/divider-free-img-1.png\" alt=\"\" />											\n							<a href=\"\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n					Facebook\n				</a>\n							<a href=\"\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n					Twitter\n				</a>\n							<a href=\"\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n					Tripadvisor\n				</a>\n							<a href=\"\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n					Instagram\n				</a>\n			<figure><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://localhost/thebbqpalace/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Zarnak-Sidhwa-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure><h3>Zarnak Sidh